headline: ENPH Q2 Deep Dive: Product Innovation and Channel Strategies Amid Tariff and Market Shifts
summary: Home energy technology company Enphase (NASDAQ:ENPH) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 19.7% year on year to $363.2 million. On the other hand, next quarter’s revenue guidance of $350 million was less impressive, coming in 5.4% below analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.69 per share was 10.8% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
